    cmd/5g, cmd/6g, cmd/8g, cmd/9g: clear Addr parameter in sudoaddable
    
    The Addr might be a stack variable with uninitialized fields.
    
    Fixes #9777.
    
    Change-Id: I799786e3d8b2e17e069725bc66a076cf9ca11f93
